{"tid":1574790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳淑莊聯合國挑機中共代表：為何中國仍安坐人權理事會？","createTime":"2019-09-16T14:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:11:40.000Z","uid":68738,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"296e36d7d5c37e5374355864d3a2c367f7734e5c","tid":1574790,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190916/720pix/1568643817_1bb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190916%2F720pix%2F1568643817_1bb8.png&h=23c50aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就在反送中運動踏入第100日之時，即將接任民主派會議新一屆發言人的公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊，應非政府組織「聯合國觀察」（UN Watch）邀請，以議員、社運人士和律師的身份，到日內瓦出席聯合國人權理事會第42次會議，在一般性辯論環節發言。陳淑莊會前率先透過Facebook表示，一定會好好把握今次機會，向全世界揭露香港警方濫權、濫暴行為持續升級的問題，希望國際社會關注香港示威者、傳媒工作者以至市民大眾的人權狀況。<br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊會上發言時指，隨着香港警隊對付示威者時使用的暴力加劇，香港正面臨人道危機，包括有被捕的示威者遭警方進行肉體上的虐待和侮辱，一名女示威者曾遭警方進行不必要和可恥的脫衣搜查；示威者被警方扣留期間，被拒絕獲得及時的醫療和法律援助；警方使用的武力亦屬過量和親疏有別，包括曾用布袋彈射盲一名救護員的眼睛，更曾襲擊無辜的地鐵乘客。<br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊指，警方至今已發射超過2,000粒催淚彈，並以「曱甴」稱呼示威者，將暴力鎮壓視為可接受的「除蟲方法（Pest control）」，藉以打壓港人言論自由。雖然反送中運動開展至今已100天，但她覺得至今沒有跡象顯示警方會收斂克制，認為這正是因為香港至今缺乏民主的惡果，令香港政府不用就警方的濫權問責。<br />\n<br />\n陳淑莊懇請聯合國人權事務高級專員（UN High Commissioner for Human Rights），支持她所提出的建議，在聯合國人權事務理事會召開緊急會議，並成立調查委員會，保障香港人的人權。陳結束發言前更挑機反問：「為何中國仍可以成員國身份，安坐在人權理事會？（Why is China sitting here as a member of this Human Rights Council？）」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190916/60051630?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F60051630%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=3b87216a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F60051630%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=791ff69f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190916/60051630?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7cde92f4f10f00b4dc663bfad29f678d879c991c","tid":1574790,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0edaa6b7c8a11306f9be37de50d1ace73db06338","tid":1574790,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=5335f75b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8bbe0a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"d6f2701c1d8279ff6d732be319a2ad0f353bbac8","tid":1574790,"uid":225050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:05:31.00